steps.userPrompt:
Review the following incident data and determine if any incidents are NOT yet acknowledged:

{{fetch-active-incidents.output}}

If ALL incidents are already acknowledged (or there are no incidents at all), use the orchestra_complete tool to stop the orchestration early with status 'success'. Otherwise, output 'Proceeding with acknowledgment'.

The following is the list of currently active IcM incidents:

{{fetch-active-incidents.output}}

For each incident that is NOT acknowledged yet in this list, find the appropriate tool in your tool list to acknowledge it, and call it. After acknowledging all incidents, output ONLY a JSON array of the incident IDs that you successfully acknowledged. The output must be a valid JSON array of numbers or strings, e.g. [12345, 67890]. Do not include any other text outside the JSON array.
